        <div class="site-header">
            <h4>Отзывы о ALBATROS SHARM RESORT (EX. BEACH ALBATROS SHARM EL SHEIKH) 4* (178)</h4>
        </div>

        <ul class="reviews-tabs nav nav-tabs">
